qas.question: How many members compose the legislature?
Is the legislature bicameral or unicameral?
How long do members serve in the legislature?
What is the head of the judicial system?
How many justices are on the Supreme Court?

context: At the legislative level, a <a1_0>unicameral<a1_0/> Assembleia Nacional Popular (National People's Assembly) is made up of <a0_0>100<a0_0/> members. They are popularly elected from multi-member constituencies to serve a <a2_0>four-year term<a2_0/>. The judicial system is headed by a <a3_0>Tribunal Supremo da Justiça (Supreme Court)<a3_0/>, made up of <a4_0>nine<a4_0/> justices appointed by the president; they serve at the pleasure of the president.
